---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="LZproxy is a worry-free business operations service built for Australian small and medium enterprises — an AI-powered 2IC for the operational functions that slow you down.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 pt-16 pb-8 md:pt-20">
    <span class="inline-flex rounded-full bg-ink/5 border border-ink/10 px-3.5 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-ink/70">
      About LZproxy
    </span>
    <h1 class="mt-6 font-[General_Sans] font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl tracking-tight">
      A second-in-command, built for how small business actually runs.
    </h1>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-8 space-y-6 text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed">
    <p>
      LZproxy is a worry-free business operations service built for Australian
      small and medium enterprises. We act as your <strong class="text-ink">Second-in-Command
      (2IC)</strong> — taking ownership of the back-office and operational
      functions that slow you down, so you can focus on growth.
    </p>
    <p>
      Every service is AI-powered at its core, and supported by experienced
      humans at every critical step. We don't just hand you a piece of
      software — we hand you a solution, and the peace of mind that comes
      with it.
    </p>
    <p>
      Most small business owners didn't start their company to spend their
      evenings reconciling invoices or chasing a super lodgement deadline.
      LZproxy exists to take that weight off — quietly, reliably, and without
      needing you to hire a whole department to do it.
    </p>
    <p>
      Our team brings more than six years of hands-on operational experience
      across <strong class="text-ink">Education, Retail, e-Commerce, Software,
      and Healthcare</strong>. That range matters — it means we've seen how
      back-office work actually breaks down in practice, not just in theory,
      across industries with very different compliance, customer, and
      operational demands. We bring that pattern-recognition to every client,
      whatever your industry.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-14">
    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-ink/10 p-8 md:p-10">
      <h2 class="font-[General_Sans] font-bold text-2xl">What makes LZproxy different</h2>
      <ul class="mt-6 space-y-4">
        {[
          ['AI backbone, human judgement', 'Automation handles the repetitive; our team handles the nuanced.'],
          ['Solution-first, not headcount-first', "You're buying an outcome, not an FTE."],
          ['Designed for Australian compliance', 'Fair Work, STP, BAS, GST, and more are built in from day one.'],
          ['Scalable tiers', 'Start with one area, grow into a full 2IC relationship.'],
          ['No lock-in at the entry tier', 'Cancel month-to-month with 30 days notice.'],
        ].map(([title, body]) => (
          <li class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-teal mt-1.5"></div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold text-ink">{title}</p>
              <p class="text-slate text-[0.95rem] mt-0.5">{body}</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 pb-24">
    <div class="rounded-3xl bg-ink text-sand px-8 py-14 md:px-14 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-[General_Sans] font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl tracking-tight">
        Curious whether LZproxy fits your business?
      </h2>
      <a href="/contact" class="mt-7 inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-amber text-ink px-7 py-3.5 font-semibold hover:brightness-95 transition">
        Book a scoping call
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
